msgid "**Source**"
msgstr "**Fuente**"

#: src/foundations/fnd-004-engineering-infrastructure.md
msgid "**Sources**: ensures dependencies come only from approved registries (crates.io, path, git with specific hosts)"
msgstr "**Fuentes**: garantiza que las dependencias provengan únicamente de registros aprobados (crates.io, path, git con hosts específicos)"

#: src/architecture/logging.md
msgid "**Spans.** Opened at entry points, walked by the layer."
msgstr "**Spans.** Se abren en los puntos de entrada y son recorridos por la capa."

