#: src/providers/configuration.md
msgid "Every model provider lives at `[providers.models.<type>.<alias>]`. `<type>` is a canonical family slot (see the [Catalog](./catalog.md#all-slots) for every slot with its endpoint). `<alias>` is your operator-assigned instance name, pick any descriptive name (`home`, `work`, `cn`, `gpt5`, ...)."
