#: src/maintainers/pr-workflow.md
msgid "Issue triage stays a shared maintainer responsibility. Accepted issues do not need a standing owner map before they can remain open, and CODEOWNERS does not make code owners responsible for every issue in a matching area."
msgstr "El triaje de issues sigue siendo una responsabilidad compartida de los maintainers. Los issues aceptados no necesitan un mapa de owners permanente para poder seguir abiertos, y CODEOWNERS no hace que los code owners sean responsables de cada issue en un área coincidente."

