#: src/ops/service.md
msgid "On macOS, the LaunchAgent (`~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.zeroclaw.daemon.plist`) sets `RunAtLoad` and `KeepAlive` to `true`, so launchd keeps the daemon running and relaunches it whenever it exits."
msgstr "En macOS, el LaunchAgent (`~/Library/LaunchAgents/com.zeroclaw.daemon.plist`) establece `RunAtLoad` y `KeepAlive` en `true`, por lo que launchd mantiene el daemon en ejecución y lo vuelve a iniciar cada vez que finaliza."

