#: src/foundations/fnd-005-contribution-culture.md
msgid "The skills being described here: giving direction clearly, evaluating output critically, understanding where a component fits in a larger system, knowing what good looks like before you build, are not AI-specific skills. They are the skills that make someone an effective engineer, an effective tech lead, and eventually an effective engineering manager."
