msgid "`zeroclaw quickstart` writes credentials to the secrets store by default. Configs you commit should not contain inline keys. For ecosystem-default names you already export in your shell (`$ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`, `$OPENROUTER_API_KEY`, …), the [env-vars reference](../reference/env-vars.md#bridging-ecosystem-default-env-vars) shows the one-line bash expansions that point a schema-mirror name at the existing value."
